name: __EPropertyBindingPermissionLevel
doc: Controls the level of support you want to have for widget property binding.

Allow: Freely allow the use of property binding.
Prevent:
Prevent any new property binding, will still allow you to edit widgets with property binding, but
the buttons will be missing on all existing widgets that don't have bindings.
PreventAndWarn: Prevent any new property binding, and warn when compiling any existing bindings.
PreventAndError: Prevent any new property binding, and error when compiling any existing bindings.
